  "pluginNotes": "Popover is a SAP instance for floating panels. Plugin places via SAP_KEYS. In design mockups, Popovers are typically shown in their open state next to (not overlapping) their trigger element — actual modal/floating overlay behavior is runtime-only and not represented in static Figma frames.",
